      <title>贝森特和特朗普再次威胁实施普遍关税，美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/dollar-climbs-as-bessent-trump-reignite-universal-tariff-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普和斯科特·贝森特就关税发表评论后，美元兑所有主要货币走强，这提振了对储备货币的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/dollar-climbs-as-bessent-trump-reignite-universal-tariff-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 23:38:12 GMT</pubDate>
