    <item>
      <title>市场关注特朗普的关税威胁，油价持续下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在本周开盘下跌 2% 之后趋于稳定，因为交易员继续关注美国总统唐纳德·特朗普可能采取的关税措施，这可能会扰乱全球经济增长和贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 23:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称预计 TikTok 将有很多竞购者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/trump-says-he-expects-a-lot-of-bidders-for-tiktok</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在佛罗里达州迈阿密特朗普国家多拉尔举行的众议院共和党会议上表示，TikTok 将吸引大量竞标者。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/trump-says-he-expects-a-lot-of-bidders-for-tiktok</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 23:27:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
